rComments: Je ne suis pas élève dans le département du théâtre, mais j'ai absolument adoré mon cours avec Professeur Gauthier. Il était très accomodant, discutait avec les étudiants, et semble très impliqué dans la communauté théâtrale locale, qui est un atout. Un cours très amusant qui fait penser!

He was honestly the most caring and funny professor I have ever had. My oral French was good but my writing was not the best. The first 2 assignments, I had a difficult time, but later for the exam and last assignment I did great and my mark really rose. He is quite specific on what he wants yet he gives you amazing notes, help and practice.

I cannot stress this enough but this professor is AMAZING!!! I normally hate history but he made me love it. He makes the subject so interesting and makes the class laugh all the while. He really wants his students to succeed and does a lot to ensure so. I wish all professors were like him. He could teach any subject and I would take the class!
